{"tid":130164,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘肉骨茶","createTime":"2017-02-22T07:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T17:40:27.000Z","uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90e14c37cdaa989e02092100c02dc8363b2e2d7b","tid":130164,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"整體都ok<br />\n湯濃,肉腍唔黐牙<br />\n係無鰂魚涌嗰間咁芳香、有層次<br />\n藥材味幾重下<br />\n熱飲無問題<br />\n放涼左有少少覺得澀口<br />\n<br />\n內有四條骨、肉丸、豆卜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/154334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F154334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=264df535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶少少肥膏<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/154413_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F154413_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=44b0c5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/154503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F154503_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a29ab7b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84773edc4e5af8902190818ba5b167be830bcc75","tid":130164,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb22ec45618db10127cd52e9ae45698c51576658","tid":130164,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"工業區熟食中心？"},{"pid":"bc610e9ce91886c995a91680f9daa98285494011","tid":130164,"uid":37442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"QB 那裏有肉骨茶?"},{"pid":"4c87237f12cc1fd4a5215bb73